Ask E. Jean: My Husband Said I Look Older Than My Older Sister|http://www.elle.com/life-love|http://www.elle.com/life-love/ask-e-jean/a23461879/ask-e-jean-my-husband-appearance/||2018-09-26|E. Jean||Dear E. Jean: My husband said I look older than my sister, who is six years older than me. I am very hurt. What should I do or say?—Wilting Here!

Wilting, My Tulip: This is a problem that has plagued women for thousands of years. Auntie Eeee has come up with a solution.

Advertisement - Continue Reading Below

1. Never believe what a husband says about your looks (unless it’s a compliment).

2. Never care what a husband says about your looks.

3. Never ask what a husband thinks about your looks.

PS: If you want a man’s opinion, ask Tim Gunn.

This article originally appeared in the October 2018 issue of ELLE.

